2 million children are victims of dog bites every year😢

You must understand that most aggressive dogs are insecure and they are insecure because they are fearful.

It is a must that you properly socialize your dogs around everything including bikes, scooters, shopping carts, vacuums, children, balls, dogs, strangers, and many more things. 

Just because you can get your dog to sit for a treat in your living room does not mean you can take your dog into a public setting with high levels of stress and stimulation so make sure you socialize your dogs, so they are ready to handle the real world especially the kiddos!
